Monday 2:28pm
Kesley- membership coordinator
Hello everyone! This will be my fourth year as a member of the UVic Ballroom Club, and my second as an executive. I never really took any formal dance training until I joined ballroom (unless you count a failed attempt at Kinder Ballet where I thought that spinning in circles by myself was much more enjoyable than paying attention in class!). Fast forward to today, and not a day goes by that I don't dance, whether it be on the social floor or at my house. That in itself is a testament to how addicting ballroom, and the club, can be. Like all the execs, I look forward to seeing you on the dance floor!

Warning: by joining the UVic Ballroom Dance Club, you must be prepared to meet fun and quirky people, learn a lifelong skill, and dance your days and nights away.
Ryan Kim
